Package: malonylcoa
Type: Package
Title: Database Utilities for MySQL Operations
Version: 1.0.0
Author: gbench
Maintainer: gbench <gbench@sina.com>
Description: A collection of database utility functions for MySQL operations including
    query execution, table creation, data insertion and updates. Provides convenient
    wrappers for common database operations with support for connection management,
    transaction handling, and SQL generation from data frames.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/gbench/malonylcoa
BugReports: https://github.com/gbench/malonylcoa/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
